207
00:23:25,590 --> 00:23:27,550
I can't believe Sanji-kun is dead...

208
00:23:27,550 --> 00:23:30,730
Why is it just you and the old
man here?! I can't rely on you!

209
00:23:30,730 --> 00:23:32,080
That's my line!

210
00:23:32,080 --> 00:23:34,350
Straw Hat! I'm going to eliminate you!

211
00:23:34,350 --> 00:23:37,870
It's no use! Your bazooka doesn't work on me!

212
00:23:37,870 --> 00:23:40,850
Wretched pest! Don't mock sky combat!

213
00:23:40,850 --> 00:23:42,480
On the next episode of One Piece!

214
00:23:42,480 --> 00:23:46,040
